#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Dreamweb (1994) is a dark cyberpunk top-down adventure by Creative Reality —"
" a disturbing journey through the Dreamweb, a mystical barrier protecting "
"reality, heavily inspired by Blade Runner."
msgstr ""
"Dreamweb (1994) é uma aventura cyberpunk da Creative Reality, uma jornada "
"perturbadora através da Dreamweb, uma barreira mística que protege a "
"realidade, fortemente inspirada por Blade Runner."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_dreamweb.html.heex:87
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Dreamweb was one of the first mainstream games to feature an uncensored sex "
"scene, which was controversial at release."
msgstr ""
