msgstr "— Alt-fire"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:61
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Ammo is shared across all bullet weapons. The chaingun is devastating but "
"burns ammo fast."
msgstr ""
"— As munições são compartilhadas em todas as armas de bala. A pistola é "
"devastadora, mas queima munições rapidamente."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:75
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:72
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Blue-uniformed SS guards deal heavy damage and move fast. Take them out "
"first."
msgstr ""
"— Guardas SS azul-uniformes lidam com danos pesados e se movem rápido. Tira-"
"os primeiro."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Break every crate you see. They often contain health kits, ammo, and "
"batteries."
msgstr ""
"- Parte todas as caixas que vires. Muitas vezes contêm kits de saúde, "
"munição e baterias."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_librequake.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Bunny hopping and strafe jumping work just like in original Quake."
msgstr "- Bunny pulando e strafe salto trabalho como no original Quake."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:53
